title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 5 categories of Defense Category on the x axis representing 2 groups: 2017/18, and 2018/19.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Defense Category Military defense with a mean value of 37194.5.
Followed by R&D defense with a mean value of 1285.0.
The lowest category is observed at Civil defense that has a mean value of 92.0
showing a difference of 199.0% with the maximum value.
In case of Military defense, 2017/18 shows more dominance than any other Defense Category and it has the lowest value in Civil defense.
